<div id="how">
  <div class="content">
    <p><strong>What Do I Do Here?</strong></p>
    <p>Enter the 5-digit number found on any bus stop to start or join the conversation about the stop and surrounding area. Use the icons at the top of the post to give your comment one or more categories.<p>

    <p>There are no user accounts or passwords, but you can sign a name to your comments after three posts (unique names are not guaranteed). Vote up the comments you like, vote down to disagree, and report offensive content.</p>

    <p><em>This Is Our Stop</em> is offered as-is. Speak your mind but no racism, sexism or spamming. Do not promote your business or website here because nobody cares. We reserve the right to erase offensive content and block devices from the service.</p> 
